WITH SOME DUMB CRIMINALS BEFORE,

14:46.179 --> 14:49.149
BUT YOU TWO? WOW.

14:49.149 --> 14:51.718
OKAY. UH,
JUST GIVE ME A DOLLAR,

14:51.718 --> 14:53.186
EACH OF YOU,
BOTH OF YOU.

14:53.186 --> 14:55.889
GIVE ME A DOLLAR,
PLEASE.

14:55.889 --> 14:57.524
