THE SEARCH WARRANT.

15:09.976 --> 15:13.179
YEAH, WELL,
I UNDERSTAND THAT.

15:13.179 --> 15:15.115
SO WHY DO YOU NEED
THE KEYS?

15:15.115 --> 15:17.751
TO TAKE POSSESSION
OF THE PROPERTY.

15:17.751 --> 15:21.755
