20:17.918 --> 20:19.419
WHERE WERE YOU?

20:19.419 --> 20:22.155
I WAS SITTING
ON THE SOFA.

20:22.155 --> 20:23.590
ON THE SOFA.

20:23.590 --> 20:25.358
YES.

20:25.358 --> 20:28.729
