OF YOUR LIFE.

21:25.626 --> 21:29.596
NOW I'M GONNA ASK YOU THIS
ONE MORE TIME, KATHERYN.

21:29.596 --> 21:30.897
WHAT HAPPENED?

21:30.897 --> 21:32.232
I SHOT THE BITCH.

21:32.232 --> 21:34.067
