21:52.619 --> 21:54.387
DON'T. SHE PUSHED ME.

21:54.387 --> 21:58.291
YOU PUSHED ME.
AND THAT DAMN VERONICA.

21:58.291 --> 22:00.160
AND I SAVED A FEW BULLETS
FOR YOU, TOO.

22:00.160 --> 22:02.836
‐OH, KATHERYN, MY GOD.
‐NO, DON'T YOU DARE.

22:02.836 --> 22:04.538
DON'T YOU DARE!

22:04.538 --> 22:07.207
I ASKED YOU TO LET WYATT PAY
FOR WHAT HE HAD DONE.

22:07.207 --> 22:09.309
AND I ASKED YOU TO HAVE
AMANDA COMMITTED.

22:09.309 --> 22:11.311
AND I ASKED YOU
TO TAKE CARE OF VERONICA.

22:11.311 --> 22:13.647
OKAY. OKAY.

22:13.647 --> 22:14.948
IT'S ALL MY FAULT.

22:14.948 --> 22:16.249
‐YES.
‐I UNDERSTAND.

22:16.249 --> 22:18.351
YES.

22:18.351 --> 22:22.322
YOU FEEL BETTER?

22:22.322 --> 22:23.824
