THAT'S WHAT WE GET.

22:27.761 --> 22:29.195
WHO KNEW
THAT SHE WAS HERE?

22:29.195 --> 22:32.766
JUST YOU, DAVID,
VERONICA, AND ME.

22:32.766 --> 22:36.603
OH, THAT'S JUST GREAT.
JUST ME, DAVID, AND VERONICA.

22:36.603 --> 22:39.239
‐ARE YOU INSANE?
‐YES.

22:39.239 --> 22:41.742
AND MAYBE I'LL USE THAT
AS MY DEFENSE.

22:41.742 --> 22:43.877
WHAT THE HELL
DOES THAT EVEN MEAN?

22:43.877 --> 22:46.112
WELL, SINCE YOU WON'T LET ME
GET RID OF VERONICA,

22:46.112 --> 22:48.148
