WITH AN INSANITY DEFENSE.

22:48.148 --> 22:49.750
AND I LIKE THAT ONE.

22:49.750 --> 22:51.818
BUT I LIKE
THIS ONE BETTER.

22:51.818 --> 22:53.119
HOW 'BOUT
I SHOOT YOU, HUH?

22:53.119 --> 22:55.989
AND YOU ‐‐

22:55.989 --> 22:57.323
YOU SHOOT YOURSELF,

22:57.323 --> 23:00.393
AND IT WAS A SUICIDAL PACT
BETWEEN YOU AND JENNIFER.

23:00.393 --> 23:02.368
NOT ME, OF COURSE.

23:02.368 --> 23:04.638
I'LL CRY FOR THE CAMERAS

23:04.638 --> 23:08.341
JUST LIKE
THAT WHORE CELINE DID.

23:08.341 --> 23:11.778
WHICH ONE OF THEM
WOULD YOU PREFER?

23:11.778 --> 23:13.213
SHE GOT BETWEEN ME

23:13.213 --> 23:17.017
AND MY ONLY LIVING CHILD.

23:17.017 --> 23:18.919
KATHERYN...

23:18.919 --> 23:21.788
I'LL HANDLE IT.

23:21.788 --> 23:23.590
WELL, YOU
DAMN WELL BETTER.

23:25.959 --> 23:28.061
AND, JIM,

23:28.061 --> 23:30.597
I WANT YOU
TO HAVE MY RUGS CLEANED.

23:30.597 --> 23:32.065
I DON'T WANT
THAT BITCH'S BODY

23:32.065 --> 23:36.336
STAINING MY $200,000 RUG.

23:36.336 --> 23:38.972
AND WHEN YOU FINISH
CLEANING UP THAT MESS,

23:38.972 --> 23:40.240
I WANT YOU
TO PACK YOUR THINGS

23:40.240 --> 23:42.709
AND GET THE HELL
OUT OF MY HOUSE!

23:49.115 --> 23:51.184
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

23:56.222 --> 23:57.223
HEY.

23:57.223 --> 23:58.892
HEY, MAN.

23:58.892 --> 24:00.967
HOW ARE YOU?

24:00.967 --> 24:02.636
GOOD.

24:02.636 --> 24:05.572
I'M GOOD.

24:05.572 --> 24:08.775
HEY, UM...

24:08.775 --> 24:11.011
LOOK, I'M SORRY.

24:11.011 --> 24:14.014
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

24:14.014 --> 24:15.381
‐YEAH.
‐YOU OKAY?

24:15.381 --> 24:18.184
THANKS.
YEAH, YEAH, I'M FINE.

24:18.184 --> 24:19.452
