YOU'RE ALL SETTLED IN.

24:28.762 --> 24:31.164
YEAH. YEAH.

24:31.164 --> 24:32.465
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

24:32.465 --> 24:35.068
[ SCOFFS ]
LOVE THE PLACE, MAN.

24:35.068 --> 24:37.504
I MEAN,
LOOK AT THIS PLACE.

24:37.504 --> 24:38.972
EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT
WITH IT?

24:38.972 --> 24:42.943
YEAH. YEAH, IT'S GREAT.

24:42.943 --> 24:44.778
SO THEN
WHY'D YOU CALL ME?

24:46.980 --> 24:48.815
LOOK, I NEED
SOME BLOW, MAN.

24:48.815 --> 24:50.116
‐WYATT.
‐LISTEN, MAN,

24:50.116 --> 24:52.418
DON'T START, ALL RIGHT?
I KNOW YOU CAN GET THE PURE.

24:52.418 --> 24:56.389
YOU ALMOST DIED.

24:56.389 --> 24:58.592
