BUT I LEARNED MY LESSON.

24:58.592 --> 25:01.502
NO, YOU DIDN'T.

25:01.502 --> 25:04.605
ARE YOU GONNA SELL TO ME OR NOT?
NO.

25:04.605 --> 25:06.873
‐WHAT?
‐I'M NOT.

25:06.873 --> 25:08.108
