25:08.108 --> 25:09.943
LOOK, I'M NOT GONNA DO IT.

25:09.943 --> 25:11.444
YOU O. D.'d, MAN.

25:11.444 --> 25:14.314
I HAD A BUDDY
THAT GOT SENT UP FOR MURDER.

25:14.314 --> 25:17.150
‐WHAT?
‐HE HAD A CLIENT THAT DIED.

25:17.150 --> 25:20.286
I'M NOT GONNA DO THAT.

25:20.286 --> 25:21.888
PETE, YOU'RE A DRUG DEALER.

25:21.888 --> 25:24.090
