ARE YOU DOING HERE?

25:30.030 --> 25:33.734
‐WYATT, GO GET SOME HELP.
‐OKAY, YOU ‐‐

25:33.734 --> 25:35.501
DO YOU THINK
THAT I NEED YOU?

25:35.501 --> 25:37.437
DO YOU THINK THAT I NEED YOU?
I'VE GOT MILLIONS.

25:37.437 --> 25:39.205
I MEAN,
LOOK AT THIS PLACE.

25:39.205 --> 25:42.375
LISTEN, I'M DOING YOU
A FAVOR.

25:42.375 --> 25:46.312
YEAH, YOU THINK YOU'RE
THE ONLY GAME IN TOWN, TOO?

25:46.312 --> 25:48.481
I KNOW I'M THE ONLY ONE
THAT YOU KNOW.

25:48.481 --> 25:50.917
YEAH. YEAH.
OKAY, OKAY.

25:52.953 --> 25:54.254
YEAH.

25:56.356 --> 25:57.524
