27:03.870 --> 27:05.806
GROWN FOLKS TALKING, BOY.

27:05.806 --> 27:07.340
OH, GROWN FOLKS?

27:07.340 --> 27:09.142
MM‐HMM.

27:09.142 --> 27:11.978
