39:58.959 --> 40:00.200
ALL RIGHT.

40:04.470 --> 40:06.673
WHAT IS IT WITH THESE WOMEN?

40:21.187 --> 40:23.356
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

40:29.229 --> 40:31.998
‐Hello?
‐Hello.

40:31.998 --> 40:34.267
HEY, I HAVEN'T HEARD
FROM YOU IN A WHILE.

40:34.267 --> 40:36.102
SORRY, I'M IN THE MIDDLE
OF SOMETHING.

40:36.102 --> 40:37.638
Oh, okay.
No ‐‐ No problem.

40:37.638 --> 40:40.941
NO, W‐WAIT, WAIT.
DON'T HANG UP.

40:40.941 --> 40:43.777
IT'S NICE
TO HEAR A KIND VOICE.

40:43.777 --> 40:45.579
THANK YOU.

40:45.579 --> 40:47.614
WELL, LISTEN, I WON'T
TAKE MUCH OF YOUR TIME.

40:47.614 --> 40:50.450
I WANTED TO THANK YOU
FOR THE FLOWERS.

40:50.450 --> 40:51.985
Flowers?

40:51.985 --> 40:53.419
YEAH.

40:53.419 --> 40:56.056
I DIDN'T SEND YOU
ANY FLOWERS.

40:56.056 --> 40:57.123
OKAY.

40:57.123 --> 40:59.159
Perhaps they're
from your other man.

40:59.159 --> 41:00.727
NO.

41:00.727 --> 41:04.470
No, these say
David Harrington.

41:04.470 --> 41:06.573
‐ERICA.
‐What?

41:06.573 --> 41:08.074
THROW THEM OUT.

41:08.074 --> 41:11.177
‐WHAT?
‐Throw them out.

41:11.177 --> 41:13.113
O‐OKAY.

41:13.113 --> 41:14.715
PUT THEM
OUTSIDE YOUR ROOM.

41:14.715 --> 41:16.717
OKAY, OKAY, I WILL.

41:16.717 --> 41:18.952
‐Now.
‐OKAY.

41:18.952 --> 41:20.486
OKAY, HOLD ON.

41:27.661 --> 41:29.630
WHAT'S THE MATTER?
YOU DON'T LIKE THE FLOWERS?

41:29.630 --> 41:30.897
WHO ARE YOU?

41:30.897 --> 41:32.699
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:32.699 --> 41:33.967
SO YOU'RE THE NEW ONE.

41:33.967 --> 41:36.136
YOU SEE?
THAT'S MY MARK.

41:36.136 --> 41:38.304
HE'S A FAVORITE
FOR THE PRESIDENTIAL ELECTION.

41:38.304 --> 41:40.541
‐AND YOU CAN GET HIM.
‐WE GONNA STAY WITH YOU TONIGHT.

41:40.541 --> 41:42.108
AND THEN
WE GOING TO THE BANK,

41:42.108 --> 41:43.844
WE GETTING
ALL THE MONEY FROM YOU.

41:43.844 --> 41:45.178
I HEARD YOU WERE
GETTING DIVORCED.

41:45.178 --> 41:46.346
YOU HEARD WRONG.

41:46.346 --> 41:48.014
WELL, ACCORDING
TO THE PAPERS I SAW FILED.

41:48.014 --> 41:50.316
‐YOU SAW PAPERS?
‐WAR IS OUT!

41:50.316 --> 41:52.318
HE'S OUT.
AND HE'S LOOKING FOR YOU.

41:52.318 --> 41:54.387
Man: <i>THERE'S A BRACELET</i>
<i>WHICH DID NOT SEEM</i>

41:54.387 --> 41:55.689
<i>TO BELONG TO THE VICTIM.</i>

41:55.689 --> 41:58.158
<i>SO THEY SHOULD BE ABLE</i>
<i>TO RUN THAT FOR DNA.</i>
